'''Bartholomaeus of Neocastro''' ({{circa}} 1240 – after 1293) was an [[Italians|Italian]] jurist, and author of a chronicle called the ''[[Historia Sicula]]'', which covers the years from 1250 to 1293.<ref>{{emc1|Angela Tomeiá|Bartholomaeus of Neocastro|144–145}}</ref><ref>{{DBI | author = Ingeborg Walter | title= Bartolomèo di Neocastro | url = http://www.treccani.it/enciclopedia/bartolomeo-da-neocastro_(Dizionario-Biografico)/ | volume = 6}}</ref>

