The '''inside/outside''' model of political reform is the organizing method/philosophy being used by the [[Progressive Democrats of America]] in its efforts to change the [[Democratic Party (United States)|Democratic Party]] but also to foster a broad [[grass-roots]] [[progressivism|progressive]] social and political movement. 

